# Project Proposal layout (SETUP Form 001)

## Scope

- **Print only** — on-screen preview in `ProjectProposalPreview.tsx` stays modern/summary layout.
- Official output via `ProjectProposalDocument` rendered at print time (`printProjectProposalPdf`).

## Document title

`SETUP Form 001 - Project Proposal Format`

## Pagination

- Physical page footers via named `@page project-proposal-sheet`:
  - `@top-center`: `Effectivity: 2025`
  - `@bottom-center`: Annex A-1 footer with `counter(page)` / `counter(pages)`
- No per-section inline footers (avoid cross-bleed with TNA forms or fixed "Page X of 20").
- `FormBlock` + `break-inside: avoid` — section titles stay with content; long tables may break across pages.

## Print path

- In-page `window.print()` via `#project-proposal-print-root` + `body.project-proposal-printing`.
- `createRoot` render (do not clone preview; do not use popup `document.write`).
- Hide portal metadata in print: no Application ID, AI/draft badges, preview signature block.

## Official sections (order)

Cover → PROJECT BACKGROUND (Company Profile with checkbox grids) → Management → Plant site → Capacity/Raw materials → MARKETING ASPECTS → TECHNOLOGICAL ASPECTS → WASTE MANAGEMENT → FINANCIAL ASPECT → RISK MANAGEMENT.

## Checkbox grids

- Organization type, profit/non-profit, MSME size: match via `isOptionChecked()` against free-text form fields.
- Business activities: 2-column grid from `PP_BUSINESS_ACTIVITY_PAIRS`; RDC specify via `prioritySectorSpecify`.

## Attachments (print slots)

- `orgChart` — Management section
- `vicinityMap` — Plant site section
- `plantLayout` — S&T intervention section
- Financial reports referenced by static note text only

